  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/bf676f16d8df40399acd00e1329729b8.poster.avif?t=1773943858\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/bf676f16d8df40399acd00e1329729b8.webm?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/bf676f16d8df40399acd00e1329729b8.mp4?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Mio, a 16-year-old high school student living in a quiet urban village in Japan.  Your mom is out of town, and a kidnapper is in town.  You are home alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/65f2d6491ab9b7754a5ca137ad336405.poster.avif?t=1773943858\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/65f2d6491ab9b7754a5ca137ad336405.webm?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/65f2d6491ab9b7754a5ca137ad336405.mp4?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You walk through residential streets, visit local shops, and attend school as part of your daily routine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/d42cae13ea07e2057b3b6f5c344afa5c.poster.avif?t=1773943858\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/d42cae13ea07e2057b3b6f5c344afa5c.webm?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/d42cae13ea07e2057b3b6f5c344afa5c.mp4?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple objectives are always displayed, but no directions are given.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instead, Mio receives photos on her phone that show real locations in the world.  By recognizing streets, alleyways, and landmarks, you must find your way on your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You always know what to do but finding where is up to you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/070608e9e25aaba3c3061b0149c4da19.poster.avif?t=1773943858\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/070608e9e25aaba3c3061b0149c4da19.webm?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/070608e9e25aaba3c3061b0149c4da19.mp4?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Features]</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ~20-minutes first-person psychological horror experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS-inspired realistic visual style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a quiet Japanese neighborhood</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple on-screen objectives without directions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No complex puzzles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please take care of Mio-chan.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/bf676f16d8df40399acd00e1329729b8.poster.avif?t=1773943858\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/bf676f16d8df40399acd00e1329729b8.webm?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/bf676f16d8df40399acd00e1329729b8.mp4?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Mio, a 16-year-old high school student living in a quiet urban village in Japan.  Your mom is out of town, and a kidnapper is in town.  You are home alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/65f2d6491ab9b7754a5ca137ad336405.poster.avif?t=1773943858\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/65f2d6491ab9b7754a5ca137ad336405.webm?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/65f2d6491ab9b7754a5ca137ad336405.mp4?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You walk through residential streets, visit local shops, and attend school as part of your daily routine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/d42cae13ea07e2057b3b6f5c344afa5c.poster.avif?t=1773943858\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/d42cae13ea07e2057b3b6f5c344afa5c.webm?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/d42cae13ea07e2057b3b6f5c344afa5c.mp4?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple objectives are always displayed, but no directions are given.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instead, Mio receives photos on her phone that show real locations in the world.  By recognizing streets, alleyways, and landmarks, you must find your way on your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You always know what to do but finding where is up to you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/070608e9e25aaba3c3061b0149c4da19.poster.avif?t=1773943858\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/070608e9e25aaba3c3061b0149c4da19.webm?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307150/extras/070608e9e25aaba3c3061b0149c4da19.mp4?t=1773943858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Features]</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ~20-minutes first-person psychological horror experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS-inspired realistic visual style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a quiet Japanese neighborhood</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple on-screen objectives without directions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No complex puzzles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please take care of Mio-chan.</strong></p>",
